high_descs: Walk to the table.
Pick up the butter knife from the table.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left to the counter.
Cut the apple sitting behind the eggs on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Set the knife on the counter to the left of the sink.
Walk back to the apple.
Pick up a piece of apple from the counter.
Turn right and bring the piece of apple to the stove.
Put the piece of apple in the pot at the back left burner of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the apple inside.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Set the pot on the counter to the left of the sink behind the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of apple in a pot on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk forward to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple into three slices.
Step to face the counter on the left side of the sink.
Place the knife on the counter to the left of the sink.
Step to the right to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Step to the right to face the stove.
Place the piece of apple into the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the apple in it on the stove.
Turn left and walk to the end of the counter and turn right to face the counter.
Place the pot with an apple in it on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To put a piece of apple in the pot on the stove and set the pot on the counter to the right of the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the wooden table on your left.
Pick up the butter knife under the spoon, on the table.
Turn to your right and go to the counter between the stove and the sink.
Cut the apple between the stove and the sink, on the counter, into slices.
Turn to your right and go to the end of the counter, just before the microwave.
Place the knife on the counter, to the right of the microwave.
Turn to your right and go back to the counter between the sink and the stove.
Pick up one of the apple slices from the counter.
Move to your right so that you are right in front of the stove.
Place the apple in the large cooking pot on the front, left burner of the stove.
Pick up the cooking pot with the apple inside, from the stove.
Turn to your left and go back to the end of the counter where the knife was left.
Place the pot with the apple inside it, on the counter, behind the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooking pot containing an apple on the counter.

high_descs: Head towards the door, then hang a right and walk over to the wooden table.
Pick up the silver butter knife next to the spoon on the wooden table.
Turn around, walk towards the fridge, then hang a left and walk over to the apple on the counter.
Slice the apple into three pieces.
Turn left and walk forwards, once at the counter past the sink stop and face right.
Stab the butter knife point down into the counter next to the other butter knife.
Turn right and walk back over to the sliced apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of sliced apple.
Turn right and walk over to the metal pot on the stove.
Place the piece of sliced apple into the metal pot.
Pick up the metal pot with the piece of sliced apple in it off the stove.
Turn left and walk back to the counter where you placed the butter knife.
Put the metal pot with the piece of sliced apple in it onto the counter behind the butter knives.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal pot with a piece of sliced apple in it onto the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the table to the right.
Pick up the completely silver knife from the table.
Turn around, walk towards the counter to the right of the stove top.
Cut the apple on the counter into pieces.
Turn left, walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn right, walk to the counter to the right of the stove top.
Take a piece of apple from the counter.
Go in front of the stove.
Put the apple into the pot on the stove.
Take the pot from the stove.
Go left to the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the pot on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with a piece of apple in it on the counter to the left of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the butter knife in front of the spoon.
Turn around, walk across the room to the fridge, turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the range.
Slice the apple on the counter to the left of the range.
Turn left and walk to the end of the counter, turn left to face the counter next to the microwave.
Set the butter knife down on the counter to the right of the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the range and face the counter.
Pick up the apple slice in the middle of the three slices.
Turn right, walk to the stove and turn left to face it.
Put the apple slice in the pot.
Pick up the pot with the apple slice in it.
Turn left and walk across the room to the counter next to the microwave.
Set the pot down in between the butter knife and the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Set the pot with the apple slice and the butter knife down on the counter next to the microwave.
